706389f-a.title: Brooklyn: Prospect Park West - Garfield Place
706389f-a.text:
28-35 Prospect Park West, west side, north from Garfield to Montgomery Places.  No. 35 is in the foreground, at the corner of Garfield Place.

August 2, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
